settings.description: Iggy's refined airship, most likely to stop Mario but maybe he just wanted a new fancier airship eh?
Mario got lost in the desert, meanwhile he finds several pipes that direct him to different places but he wants to cross the barrier once and for all.
Mario explores a dense world and was trapped by some ghosts from a very haunted mansion, in which he falls from the bottom and Mairo tries to climb to the top to find his most beloved home
